---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/")
  ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL
  : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
---

<section class="px-6 py-24 md:px-10 lg:px-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-500">
        Learning approach
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-950 md:text-5xl">
        Conceptual clarity, software practice and research interpretation.
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-600">
        Support is designed around understanding the method, applying it in
        appropriate software, and explaining results clearly in an academic or
        research context.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-neutral-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src={`${base}images/data-analysis.jpg`}
            alt="Statistical analysis displayed on a laptop screen"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover grayscale"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-950">
            Statistics and data analysis
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-500">
            Support with statistical concepts, data preparation, modelling,
            visualisation and interpretation of results.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-neutral-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src={`${base}images/online-learning.jpg`}
            alt="Online learning setup with laptop and notebook"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover grayscale"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-950">
            Guided academic learning
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-500">
            Topic-based explanations, worked examples, software demonstrations
            and organised learning pathways.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-neutral-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src={`${base}images/bioinformatics.jpg`}
            alt="DNA structure representing bioinformatics and omics analysis"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover grayscale"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-950">
            Bioinformatics and omics
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-500">
            Support with biological data analysis, omics concepts, computational
            workflows and interpretation of biological outputs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>